I don&#39;t see how posting a prediction only you can confirm has any bearing on demonstrating anything other than that you believe.  It means nothing else.

If you have a post with a prediction we can all confirm, I&#39;d love to hear it.  

Before it is supposed to happen, with a date it is supposed to happen, and exactly what is to happen, of course.

We&#39;ve already got lots of end-of-the-world stuff from Frank on 2012.  So we can skip those.  We can measure that validity of that in 2012.



